ws/india/2019/05/16/India-second-Scorpene-class-sub-INS-Khanderi-induction-delayed.html |work=The Week |date=16 May 2019 |language=en |access-date=27 May 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517070355/https://www.theweek.in/news/india/2019/05/16/India-second-Scorpene-class-sub-INS-Khanderi-induction-delayed.html |archive-date=17 May 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Janes2019\">{{cite web |title=Aero India 2019: India to receive second Scorpene-class submarine by April 2019 |url=https://www.janes.com/article/86770/aero-india-2019-india-to-receive-second-scorpene-class-submarine-by-april-2019 |website=Jane's 360 |publisher=Jane's Navy International |accessdate=22 February 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190222123754/https://www.janes.com/article/86770/aero-india-2019-india-to-receive-second-scorpene-class-submarine-by-april-2019 |archivedate=22 February 2019 |date=21 February 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>|| Vishakhapatnam / Mumbai\n|-\n| S-23 || {{INS|Karanj|2018|6}}  ||  {{IND}}  || December 2012|| 31 January 2018<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=176011|title=Third Scorpene submarine \u2018Karanj\u2019 Launched at Mazagon Docks|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2018-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201075149/http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=176011|archive-date=2018-02-01|url-status=live}}</ref> || Late 2019 (expected)<ref name=\"induction_delayed\"/><ref name=\"Janes2019\"/><ref name=\"Mazagon_deliver\">{{cite news |title=Mazagon Dock to deliver second Scorpene class submarine by year end |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/mazagon-to-deliver-second-scorpene-class-submarine-by-year-end-5344023/ |accessdate=12 September 2018 |publisher=The Indian Express |date=7 September 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913020830/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/mazagon-to-deliver-second-scorpene-class-submarine-by-year-end-5344023/ |archive-date=13 S